{
  "stem": "19923.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And usually what-- what happened after you fell asleep, you fell into the middle of the bed and two of you slept on the cot.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was made so that there-- there would be room for people to sleep right between the cot and you would have to sleep there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, in the wintertime, you didn't have any heat so the blankets is all you had.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Another thing that I wanted to bring to your attention is that we didn't have any shoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were given wooden shoes called sabot, S-A-B-O-T.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we wore sabot and we became quite good at them in southern France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when you first got them, they gave you a little insert, cloth insert.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they became impractical because they got full of ice and snow and you wind up just putting your feet into the sabot without socks and walking in the middle of the winter with those and with ice and water forming in them.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But you-- as a child, you learned how-- how to maneuver on those and that's what we had as shoes in southern France.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We didn't have any clothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had shorts, we didn't have any long pants.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in terms of warm clothing, they started knitting their own sweaters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I learned how to knit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, there's a picture of me somewhere where it shows a sweater that was knit with my help also that I wore in the winter of 1940-41 in Seyre et Nailloux.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a-- we didn't starve to death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't have any food, but we were able to survive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were undernourished, there's no question about that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we didn't have much, if anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I do have one recollection, a vivid recollection.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
